# Cross-origin isolation enables tesseract.js multi-threaded WASM (faster OCR).
# `credentialless` (not `require-corp`) lets the CDN-hosted language data load
# without a CORP header. Chromium isolates and goes multi-threaded; Safari
# ignores credentialless and falls back to single-threaded (still works).
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
